title: Bug 121682: Exception thrown when exporting data from a table containing highlight/map.
description: Exception is thrown when attempting to export data from the attached report.
OB: Upon attempting to export data from a table containing highlight/map in the attached report, an exception is thrown.
EB: When exporting data from the table, the expected result is that the data should be successfully exported. However, the actual result is an exception thrown in: ReportEngineService.getMetaData().
SR:
Steps to Reproduce:
1. Open the attached report.
2. Navigate to the table containing highlight/map.
3. Attempt to export the data from the table.
4. Observe the exception being thrown in: ReportEngineService.getMetaData().
